 image, and it helps us and our advertising partners understand how you use our site. In essence, a web beacon enables two websites to share information. We and our advertising partners may use both of these technologies to help deliver advertisements about products and services that interest you. These technologies do not store any personally identifiable information about you, like your name, phone number, address, or email address. You can instruct your browser to refuse all cookies or to indicate when a cookie is being sent. However, if you do not accept cookies, you may not be able to use some portions of our website.

