 BOOTHBAY FUND Overview



												   Boothbay Fund Management Llc is a hedge fund that manages 342 MM dollars in regulatory AUM and has 7 employees, of which 3 perform investment advisory functions. The manager's has disclosed holdings from 12/31/14 to 03/31/17. The fund's latest filing disclosed 398MM in positions, representing 117% of the manager's regulatory AUM.
												



